{"tid":1226380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家嘅文宣係好有用，零零後都會收到","createTime":"2019-06-15T11:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T10:28:18.000Z","uid":61201,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b0baca5d5ae8fe1b0f7645b315699ab2edc25b0b","tid":1226380,"uid":61201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:20:32.000Z","msg":"大家嘅文宣係好有用，希望大家唔好氣餒<br />\n真係會傳到去每一個香港人手上<br />\n我係個中學老師，中一班主任<br />\n同我班啲學生有一個群組<br />\n佢哋好多背景都係新移民/草根階層<br />\n零零後本身真係乜嘢都唔知<br />\n亦都唔會明白你哋講乜嘢，只係玩抖音為樂<br />\n平時佢哋完全唔會討論任何時事<br />\n但係今次連佢哋都好留意反送中發展<br />\n今次佢哋(包括新移民)亦都有轉發一d圖同埋改歌去班group<br />\n亦都有upload d譴責政府嘅圖上IG，轉social media icon去支持<br />\n希望大家唔好放棄任何一個機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5b95a1c4a6ddb8aadc0efa1c4f27c7d4f26a71","tid":1226380,"uid":61201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:45:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e77f1bdaf56373c50fd86c2d673a6867840ae5","tid":1226380,"uid":61201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731f8d04eddebff623652d640515a8058f2746c0","tid":1226380,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:26:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c51d3dae075cbeb122e689b4977330235595c57","tid":1226380,"uid":25044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:28:18.000Z","msg":"推 今次有出既都有幾多00後"}]}